high_descs: Go left around to the other side of the round table.
Pick the pan up from the table.
Go across the room and turn to the right to stand in front of the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the pan up from the sink.
Go left to stand in front of the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the pan in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk around to the opposite side of the dining table.
Pick up the plate which is to the left of the lettuce.
Walk around the table to the refrigerator, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the plate in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn left and walk forward to the microwave above the stove top.
Put the plate in the microwave and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned plate in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward around to the far side of the round table
Pick up the dirty plate near the lettuce from the table
Walk around the table into the kitchen and over to the sink
Wash the plate under water in the sink then remove it
Turn left and walk to the microwave above the stove
Put the plate into the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the washed plate in the microwave
